00:49:26,249 --> 00:49:29,400
Just smile at the birdie,
and boom! You're in.

680
00:49:30,249 --> 00:49:36,358
Name in all the papers. Big stars
sending you pretty dresses for nothing.

681
00:49:36,529 --> 00:49:38,281
That was terrific tonight.

682
00:49:38,649 --> 00:49:40,879
You bet it was terrific.

683
00:49:41,049 --> 00:49:43,517
Best goodbye music
I ever danced to.

684
00:49:46,849 --> 00:49:49,488
Yeah, tonight was really terrific.

685
00:49:49,649 --> 00:49:53,358
See a thing like that happen
right under your eyes.

686
00:49:53,529 --> 00:49:56,760
Something you wanted for someone
all their life.

687
00:49:56,929 --> 00:49:59,682
You haven't known me all my life.

688
00:49:59,849 --> 00:50:02,488
Six months then.

689
00:50:03,449 --> 00:50:04,802
Seven.

690
