<i>John, that's the name of my finance</i>
<i>You see</i>

886
01:03:06,729 --> 01:03:08,720
<i>There's no mistak e</i>

887
01:03:08,889 --> 01:03:12,325
<i>He's very fond of me</i>

888
01:03:12,969 --> 01:03:17,884
<i>He took me out for walks</i>
<i>And, oh, he was so nice</i>

889
01:03:18,049 --> 01:03:21,007
<i>He always used to kiss me</i>

890
01:03:21,169 --> 01:03:24,844
<i>On the same place twice</i>

891
01:03:25,009 --> 01:03:30,481
<i>Often in the park</i>
<i>We would sit and spoon</i>

892
01:03:30,649 --> 01:03:33,561
<i>And I was, oh, so happy</i>

893
01:03:33,729 --> 01:03:39,326
<i>Till the other afternoon</i>

894
01:03:40,609 --> 01:03:45,364
<i>John took me round to see his mother</i>

895
01:03:45,529 --> 01:03:50,284
<i>His mother</i>
<i>His mother</i>

896
01:03:50,449 --> 01:03:54,522
<i>And when he introduced us</i>
<i>To each other</i>

897
01:03:54,689 --> 01:03:59,046
<i>She weighed up everything that I had on</i>

898
01:03:59,209 --> 01:04:04,078
<i>She put me through a cross-examination</i>

899
01:04:04,249 --> 01:04:08,879
<i>I fairly boiled with aggravation</i>

900
01:04:09,049 --> 01:04:11,324
<i>Then she shook her head</i>

901
01:04:11,489 --> 01:04:14,128
<i>Look ed at me and said:</i>

